These are Puzzles for 7x2 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 7x2-Level-1-1::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: soy-milk, coffee
The people have 2 different hobbies: card-games, skydiving
The people have 2 different jobs:  doctor, scientist
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: epic, crime
There are 2 different nationalities: indian, egyptian
2 different pets are kept: rat, guinea-pig
The people use 2 different means of transport: skateboard, tram
1. the person drinking soy-milk is on the far right##1
2. the scientist is on the far right##1
3. the person driving the tram is on the left of the person who's hobby is skydiving##1
4. the owner of the rat is the egyptian##1
5. the person watching crime movies is on the far left##1
6. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the right of the person driving the tram##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |
| Beverage      | coffee     | soy-milk       |
| Hobby         | card-games   | skydiving     |
| Job           | doctor | scientist   |
| Movie-Genre   | crime   | epic  |
| Nationality   | egyptian | indian |
| Pet           | rat      | guinea-pig     |
| Transport     | tram    | skateboard   |

