.:: Puzzle 7x2-Level-1-2::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: lemonade, soy-milk
The people have 2 different hobbies: collecting, rock-climbing
The people have 2 different jobs:  lawyer, electrician
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: metal, techno
There are 2 different nationalities: russian, brazilian
2 different pets are kept: fish, chinchilla
The people use 2 different means of transport: car, skateboard
1. the electrician is on the right of the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##1
2. the owner of the chinchilla is the person driving the skateboard##1
3. the person driving the car is on the left of the fan of metal##1
4. the brazilian is on the far right##1
5. the person drinking lemonade is the owner of the fish##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1        |    2     |
| Beverage      | lemonade    | soy-milk |
| Hobby         | rock-climbing        | collecting  |
| Job           | lawyer | electrician  |
| Music-Genre   | techno            | metal    |
| Nationality   | russian     | brazilian   |
| Pet           | fish         | chinchilla    |
| Transport     | car           | skateboard      |

